channel.title: Nice to Meet Ya!
channel.description:
My name is Anthony and I am a Software Engineer with a few SAAS products in development (don't worry, one at a time for now :wink:). My current project is an event social network since I hate missing events I would have gone to.
I look forward to learning with all of you :slight_smile:
